OL,3,CPolice say use of force when officers
OL,4,Cclashed with girls was 'justified'
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police say the use of
OL,7,Fforce in an incident which saw
OL,8,Fofficers clash with a group of teenage
OL,9,Fgirls was "proportionate, necessary,
OL,10,Fand justified."
OL,12,FIn a video shared widely on social
OL,13,Fmedia, officers appear to shove and
OL,14,Fstrike girls wearing party dresses on
OL,15,Fa street in Rotherham.
OL,17,FOne officer draws a baton and two
OL,18,Fothers brandish Tasers as they are
OL,19,Fconfronted by a group of young people.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1782402489
OL,3,CPolice say use of force when officers
OL,4,Cclashed with girls was 'justified'
OL,6,FThe South Yorkshire Mayor Oliver
OL,7,FCoppard said on Tuesday he was
OL,8,F"appalled" by the footage.
OL,10,FBut in a statement on Tuesday evening,
OL,11,FSouth Yorkshire said: "As is often the
OL,12,Fcase, the clip which has been posted
OL,13,Fon social media shows only a few
OL,14,Fseconds of a much longer police
OL,15,Fresponse to a 999 call - reporting a
OL,16,Ffight involving many young people.
OL,18,F"Having viewed the clip in isolation,
OL,19,Fit is understandable that local and
OL,20,Fwider communities have some concerns.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1782402489
OL,3,CPolice say use of force when officers
OL,4,Cclashed with girls was 'justified'
OL,6,F"Our Professional Standards Department
OL,7,Fhas now reviewed all available
OL,8,Ffootage, including Body Worn Video,
OL,9,Fand written accounts from all officers.
OL,11,F"The assessment has determined that
OL,12,Fthere is an opportunity for learning
OL,13,Faround de-escalation but, considering
OL,14,Fwhat happened before and during the
OL,15,Fclip, the use of force was
OL,16,Fproportionate, necessary, and
OL,17,Fjustified to keep all involved safe."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
