CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1782402489
OL,3,CPolice say use of force when officers
OL,4,Cclashed with girls was 'justified'
OL,6,FThe force added that it had taken the
OL,7,F"unprecedented step" of requesting
OL,8,Fpeer review from another police force
OL,9,Fwhich had upheld the decision.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
